OL,3,CManchester City parade: Route, timings
OL,4,Cand road closures
OL,6,FManchester City will mark the
OL,7,Fachievements of its men's, women's,
OL,8,Fand academy teams with an open-top bus
OL,9,Fparade through the streets of
OL,10,FManchester.
OL,12,FPep Guardiola's side secured a
OL,13,Fhistoric domestic cup double, even
OL,14,Fthough they narrowly missed out on the
OL,15,FPremier League title - finishing
OL,16,Fsecond behind Arsenal. It will also be
OL,17,FPep's final parade after announcing
OL,18,Fhis departure.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
