OL,3,CManchester City parade: Route, timings
OL,4,Cand road closures
OL,6,FWhen is the Manchester City parade?
OL,8,FThe open-top bus parade will take
OL,9,Fplace on Monday, 25 May. The key
OL,10,Ftimings for the event are:
OL,12,FWhat is the parade route?
OL,14,FThe celebrations will kick-off moment
OL,15,Fin the Northern Quarter. From there,
OL,16,Fthe open-top buses will travel through
OL,17,FAncoats before approaching the Etihad
OL,18,FStadium along Ashton New Road.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
