OL,3,CManchester City parade: Route, timings
OL,4,Cand road closures
OL,6,FThe parade will officially finish
OL,7,Foutside the stadium at The Colin Bell
OL,8,FStand Reception.
OL,10,FThe club has noted that more detailed
OL,11,Finformation on the full parade route
OL,12,F"will follow in due course."
OL,14,FWhich roads will be closed?
OL,16,FClosures from 9:00 AM to 9:00 PM
OL,17,F(Northern Quarter / Assembly Area)
OL,19,FClosures from 2:00pm to 9:00pm
OL,20,F(Ancoats & Inner Ring Road)
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
