PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779711071
OL,3,CManchester City parade: Route, timings
OL,4,Cand road closures
OL,6,FClosures from 3:00 PM to 9:00 PM
OL,7,F(Route to the Etihad)
OL,9,FDo I need a ticket?
OL,11,FNo. The City Parade is free to attend
OL,12,Fand no tickets are required.
OL,14,FFans can join the celebrations at
OL,15,Fvarious points along the route.
OL,16,FHowever, supporters should note that
OL,17,Fthey will only be able to attend one
OL,18,Fcelebration event on the day.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
