OL,3,CManchester City parade: Route, timings
OL,4,Cand road closures
OL,6,FThe parade is running at the exact
OL,7,Fsame time as The After Party at the Co-
OL,8,Fop Live - a separate event taking
OL,9,Fplace that will feature live music,
OL,10,Fentertainment, special guests, and
OL,11,Fplayer interviews.
OL,13,FHow do I get there and is there
OL,14,Fparking?
OL,16,FIf you are planning to watch the
OL,17,Fparade finish at the Etihad Stadium,
OL,18,Forganisers strongly recommend using
OL,19,Fpublic transport.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
