OL,3,CManchester City parade: Route, timings
OL,4,Cand road closures
OL,6,FWhat accessible viewing options are
OL,7,Favailable?
OL,9,FThere will be two designated
OL,10,Faccessible viewing areas along the
OL,11,Froute for wheelchair users, ambulant
OL,12,Fdisabled supporters, and their
OL,13,Fpersonal assistants or companions:
OL,15,FManchester City has reminded all
OL,16,Fattending fans that they have a
OL,17,Fresponsibility to act as ambassadors
OL,18,Ffor both the club and the City of
OL,19,FManchester.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
