OL,3,CManchester City parade: Route, timings
OL,4,Cand road closures
OL,6,FSupporters are asked to treat the
OL,7,Flocal area, and everyone else in
OL,8,Fattendance, with respect.
OL,10,FThe full forecast for the parade can
OL,11,Fbe found on the ITV News Granada
OL,12,FReports weather page.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
